    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute gem of a car. Honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this beauty since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stayed in pristine shape. It\u2019s a total dream to drive and I\u2019m really sad to see it go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. You won't find another one this clean! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
